overview.longBusinessSummary: Millrose purchases and develops residential land and sells finished homesites to home builders by way of option contracts with predetermined costs and takedown schedules. Millrose serves as a solution for home builders seeking to expand access to finished homesites while implementing an asset-light strategy. As fully developed homesites are sold by Millrose, capital is recycled into future land acquisitions for home builders, providing customers with durable access to community growth.
